      <title>Verizon希望出售高级笔记以资助债务赎回</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/verizon-looks-to-sell-high-grade-notes-to-fund-debt-redemption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Verizon Communications Inc.计划在周一出售投资级公司债券，部分原因是为了资助明年应付款近10亿美元的票据。]]></description>
